          "back": "We have  \\[\\frac{\\phantom{o}\\frac1y\\phantom{o}}{\\frac1x} = \\frac{1}{y} \\cdot \\frac{x}{1} = \\frac{x}{y} = \\boxed{\\frac{2}{3}}.\\]",
          "hint": "Category: Algebra, Difficulty: 2/5"
