          "back": "Because $\\sqrt{16}<\\sqrt{17}<\\sqrt{25}$, or, $4<\\sqrt{17}<5$, the largest integer less than $\\sqrt{17}$ is $4$. Therefore, $4^2=\\boxed{16}$.",
