          "front": "The operation $\\star$ is defined as $a \\star b = a + \\frac{a}{b}$. What is the value of $12 \\star 3$?",
          "back": "We have $12 \\star 3 = 12+ \\frac{12}{3}=12+4=\\boxed{16}$.",
          "hint": "Category: Algebra, Difficulty: 1/5"
