          "front": "Find the fraction that equals $0.\\overline{73}$.",
          "back": "We have \\[0.\\overline{73} = \\frac{73}{100} + \\frac{73}{10000} + \\frac{73}{1000000} + \\cdots.\\]This infinite geometric series has first term $73/100$ and common ratio $1/100$, so we have \\[0.\\overline{73} = \\frac{73/100}{1-1/100} = \\boxed{\\frac{73}{99}}.\\]",
