          "content": "**Problem (Algebra, Level 3):**\nConsider the function $g(x)=3x-4$.  For what value of $a$ is $g(a)=0$?\n\n**Solution:**\nSince $g(a) = 3a-4$, the equation $g(a)=0$ means $3a-4=0$.  Solving this equation gives $a = \\boxed{\\frac{4}{3}}$.",
