          "back": "This is an infinite geometric series with first term $a=1$ and common ratio $r=\\frac{1}{3}$. Thus the sum is: $$\\frac{a}{1-r} = \\frac{1}{1-\\frac13} = \\frac{1}{\\frac{2}{3}}=\\boxed{\\frac{3}{2}}.$$",
