          "back": "\\begin{align*}\n2^{x-3} &= 4^{x+1} \\\\\n2^{x-3} &= (2^2)^{x+1} \\\\\n2^{x-3} &= 2^{2x+2} \\\\\nx-3 &= 2x+2 \\\\\nx &= \\boxed{-5}\n\\end{align*}",
