          "front": "Evaluate $\\left\\lfloor -\\frac{5}{3}\\right\\rfloor.$",
          "back": "$-\\frac{5}{3}$ is between $-2$ and $-1$, so $\\left\\lfloor -\\frac{5}{3}\\right\\rfloor = \\boxed{-2}$.",
