          "front": "Evaluate $\\left\\lceil\\left(-\\frac{5}{3}\\right)^2\\right\\rceil$.",
          "back": "The expression inside the ceiling brackets evaluates to $$\\left(-\\frac{5}{3}\\right)^2 = \\frac{25}{9} = 3 - \\frac{2}{9}$$Since this is an integer minus a non-negative number less than one, the ceiling of it equals the integer, $\\boxed{3}$.",
