          "back": "Note that $a-2 = 0$, since $a = 2$.  Thus the product in question is \\[ (a -10) \\dotsm (a-3) \\cdot (a-2) \\cdot (a-1) \\cdot a = (a-10) \\dotsm (a-3) \\cdot 0 \\cdot (a-1) \\cdot a, \\] which is $\\boxed{0}$, since zero times any real number is zero.",
