          "title": "Simplify $(3-2i)-(5-2i)$.",
          "content": "**Problem (Algebra, Level 2):**\nSimplify $(3-2i)-(5-2i)$.\n\n**Solution:**\n$(3-2i)- (5-2i) = 3-2i -5+2i = (3-5) + (-2i+2i) = \\boxed{-2}$.",
