          "id": "math-c9dbf83d845dbb17",
          "front": "The ratio $\\frac{10^{2000}+10^{2002}}{10^{2001}+10^{2001}}$ is closest to which whole number?",
          "back": "We have $$\n\\frac{10^{2000} + 10^{2002}}{10^{2001} + 10^{2001}}=\n\\frac{{10^{2000}(1 + 100)}}{{10^{2000}(10 + 10)}} = \\frac{101}{20}\\approx \\boxed{5}.\n$$",
          "hint": "Category: Algebra, Difficulty: 4/5"
