          "title": "Compute $139+27+23+11$.",
          "content": "**Problem (Algebra, Level 1):**\nCompute $139+27+23+11$.\n\n**Solution:**\nSince addition is associative, we can rearrange the terms:\n\n$139+27+23+11=(139+11)+(27+23)=150+50=\\boxed{200}$.",
