          "front": "Evaluate $\\lfloor\\sqrt{80}\\rfloor$.",
          "back": "Since $\\sqrt{64}<\\sqrt{80}<\\sqrt{81}$, $\\sqrt{80}$ must be a number between $8$ and $9$. Therefore, the greatest integer that is less than or equal to $\\sqrt{80}$ is $\\boxed{8}$.",
