          "front": "Which integer is closest to the cube root of 100?",
          "back": "Either 4 or 5 is closest to $\\sqrt[3]{100}$, since $4^3=64$ and $5^3=125$.  Since $4.5^3=91.125<100$, $\\sqrt[3]{100}$ is closer to $\\boxed{5}$ than to 4.",
          "hint": "Category: Algebra, Difficulty: 1/5"
