          "id": "math-283c30a34c1c843b",
          "front": "Define $A\\star B$ as $A\\star B = \\frac{(A+B)}{3}$. What is the value of $(2\\star 10) \\star 5$?",
          "back": "We have $2 \\star 10 = \\frac{2+10}{3} = \\frac{12}{3} = 4$. Then $4 \\star 5 = \\frac{4+5}{3} = \\frac{9}{3} = \\boxed{3}$.",
          "hint": "Category: Algebra, Difficulty: 2/5"
