          "id": "math-456624d15c44b3fe",
          "front": "Evaluate $\\frac{3+x(3+x)-3^2}{x-3+x^2}$ for $x=-2$.",
          "back": "$\\frac{3+x(3+x)-3^2}{x-3+x^2}=\\frac{3+(-2)(3+(-2))-3^2}{-2-3+(-2)^2}=\\frac{-8}{-1}=\\boxed{8}$",
