          "id": "math-c-23d5bee4422198e7",
          "title": "Evaluate $\\log_2\\frac{1}{16}$.",
          "content": "**Problem (Algebra, Level 2):**\nEvaluate $\\log_2\\frac{1}{16}$.\n\n**Solution:**\nLet $x=\\log_2\\frac{1}{16}$.  Then, we must have $2^x = \\frac{1}{16} = 2^{-4}$, so $x=\\boxed{-4}$.",
