          "id": "math-a315f5ba20a1f8b6",
          "front": "When the square root of $x$ is cubed, the answer is 64. What is the value of $x$?",
          "back": "We have $(\\sqrt{x})^3=64$ and solve for $x$. $$x^\\frac{3}{2}=64\\qquad\\Rightarrow x=64^\\frac{2}{3}=(64^\\frac{1}{3})^2=4^2=16$$The value of $x$ is $\\boxed{16}$.",
